channel.title: Need help! I compiled my server... Now what?
channel.description:
I compiled my server and I have no-ip opened. I have testscape source and when i click run.bat it appears this text:
"Starting testscape server on 0.0.0.0:43594"
What do i do? I really don't know what to do after compiling the server! Please help me out! If possible explain all steps I have to do to put server up for people to play on it!
